data.description: "Welcome to your spacious slice of paradise in Cape Coral! This charming 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is nestled on an oversized corner lot, offering ample space and privacy. With its versatile layout and abundant natural light, this property is perfect for both relaxing and entertaining. Enjoy the convenience of a well-appointed kitchen, cozy living areas, and a serene outdoor oasis. Whether you're dreaming of lazy afternoons in the sun or hosting gatherings with loved ones, this home promises comfort and tranquility. Don't  miss the opportunity to make this your own piece of Florida paradise!"
